For full inventory runs, TLO uses TLOHome/toBeInventoried.txt unless a Search Path override is supplied in the GUI or with --search-path on the command line. Prepare this file before the run when you are not using a one-time Search Path override. Each non-comment line is one inventory root. Blank lines and lines whose first non-whitespace character is # are ignored. Lines beginning with REM are also treated as comments.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af12\afs22\alang1025 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe1033\hich\af2\loch\sl276\slmult1\ql\widctlpar\hyphpar0\sb0\sa200\ltrpar\cf0\f2\fs20\lang1033\kerning0\dbch\af10\langfe1033\sl276\slmult1{\loch
