Tag Copy/Delete Original -- Destination Path is a global full-inventory override. When filled, it overrides any per-path --$copy or --$copy-delete destination from toBeInventoried.txt. If Search Path is empty, TLO checks that this one destination can hold the combined source size of all accessible roots in toBeInventoried.txt before the run starts. During the run, TLO still reads the original folders for artist/date/show metadata, but successful copy/delete originals are inventoried at the destination.}
\par \pard\plain \s76\loch\sl240\slmult1\sb0\sa200\contextualspace{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af12 \ltrch \u61623\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls1 \fi-360\li360\lin360\sl240\slmult1{\hich\af7\loch\f7\loch
